Dear Harshit,
It was a very good time of around 3 years which we had spent together.Tu nahi hota toh the fun quotient of the  wing would have dropped significantly. I remember the first sem ka Harshit jo rota rehta tha and since then there was no looking back uske baad toh bas daase aur pranks aur masti hi hai to look forward. Last but not the least the parties jaha # kanuumerikanuu #Tpkobulao and #AkshatMadarchod famous hue the . I still don't know maine kya kiya tha to deserve that. I have our paths cross again. 


Till that P**ma Lmao

Thank You,
